1. Vi *pokušavate* da me ubedite u svoje mišljenje. (You are *trying* to persuade me into your opinion.)
2. Ne uspevate da *pokušate* dovoljno jako. (You are not succeeding in *trying* hard enough.)
3. *Pokušavate* da rešite problem na pogrešan način. (You are *trying* to solve the problem in the wrong way.)
4. Da li *pokušavate* da mi kažete da ne možete da dođete na sastanak? (Are you *trying* to tell me that you can't come to the meeting?)
5. Kako *pokušavate* da se nosite sa stresom na poslu? (How are you *trying* to cope with work stress?)
6. Ukoliko *pokušavate* da smršate, trebalo bi da se bavite fizičkom aktivnošću. (If you are *trying* to lose weight, you should engage in physical activity.)
7. Oni *pokušavaju* da pronađu način da smanje troškove proizvodnje. (They are *trying* to find a way to reduce production costs.)
8. Ne znam zašto *pokušavate* da me uverite da je to nemoguće. (I don't know why you are *trying* to convince me that it's impossible.)
9. Molim vas da *pokušate* da budete precizniji u svojim izjavama. (Please *try* to be more precise in your statements.)
10. Nema potrebe da *pokušavate* da me impresionirate, već samo recite istinu. (There's no need to *try* to impress me, just tell the truth.)